coming from a pharmacist.</i>

00:15.140 --> 00:16.349
<i>[Jackson]</i> <i>Someone
broke in through my back door.</i>

00:16.391 --> 00:17.350
<i>For a guy who says</i>

00:17.392 --> 00:19.185
<i>he doesn't handle much fentanyl,</i>

00:19.227 --> 00:20.770
