<i>If I were you, I might put
a camera out back there.</i>

00:23.356 --> 00:26.359
<i>And I'll use Jackson to get
to this Bobby Jesus prick.</i>

00:26.401 --> 00:28.319
<i>You want to find this Bobby guy
for your girlfriend.</i>

00:28.361 --> 00:30.030
<i>You tag him with drug dealing
and killing</i>

00:30.071 --> 00:31.823
<i>a high school kid, he becomes
a pretty terrible witness</i>

00:31.865 --> 00:33.158
<i>against Billy Poe.</i>

00:33.199 --> 00:34.409
<i>You can have
two different reasons</i>

00:34.451 --> 00:36.036
<i>-for doing the right thing.
- No.</i>

00:36.077 --> 00:37.412
<i>If it's the wrong reason,
it corrupts everything.</i>

00:37.454 --> 00:39.039
<i>The guy who named Billy
is a drug dealer?</i>

00:39.080 --> 00:42.000
<i>-Can you prove it?
- Not yet, but I'm trying.</i>

00:42.042 --> 00:43.543
<i>Don't worry.
You'll figure it out.</i>

00:43.585 --> 00:45.003
<i>We're in this together.</i>

00:45.045 --> 00:46.421
<i>Lawyer's here, Poe. Let's go.</i>

00:46.463 --> 00:47.589
<i>Tell her to go home.
I'm not interested.</i>

00:47.630 --> 00:49.132
<i>You protecting somebody?</i>

00:50.425 --> 00:51.718
<i>Please don't.
Please don't hit me.</i>

00:51.760 --> 00:53.553
<i>It's okay. Hey.</i>

00:53.595 --> 00:55.722
<i>It's Rachel.
Public defender Rachel.</i>

00:55.764 --> 00:57.932
<i>Oh. Shit. Hi.</i>

00:57.974 --> 00:59.642
<i>Your son is refusing to see me.</i>

00:59.684 --> 01:01.728
<i>I can't be his lawyer
until he signs the paper.</i>

01:01.770 --> 01:03.146
<i>I can get you in to talk to him.</i>

01:03.188 --> 01:04.230
<i>How do you know that?</i>

01:04.272 --> 01:05.857
<i>Because he's in love with me.</i>

01:05.899 --> 01:08.485
<i>I just want to know
how much he's willing to pay you</i>

01:08.526 --> 01:12.072
<i>to come here and talk us out
of what's owed to us.</i>

01:12.113 --> 01:13.073
<i>Enough, Grace!</i>

01:13.114 --> 01:14.240
<i>Felonies make up</i>

01:14.282 --> 01:15.909
<i>a big chunk of the population.</i>

01:15.950 --> 01:18.328
<i>And you're a big guy.
Someone'll test you.</i>

01:18.369 --> 01:21.247
<i>Do not engage.
You hear me, Billy?</i>

01:27.212 --> 01:29.214
<i>dramatic music</i>

01:36.262 --> 01:37.806
<i>-Okay.</i>

01:39.182 --> 01:40.600
<i>What?</i>

01:40.642 --> 01:42.936
<i>Can you ask Rylan
to shut off the music?</i>

01:42.977 --> 01:44.479
<i>-Will he do that?
- He better.</i>

01:44.521 --> 01:46.231
<i>Considering what I laid out
for all this beer.</i>

01:46.272 --> 01:48.566
<i>Okay.</i>

01:48.608 --> 01:51.152
<i>-</i>

01:56.116 --> 01:57.826
<i>All right.</i>

01:59.369 --> 02:01.621
<i>Hey! Listen up, everyone!</i>

02:05.125 --> 02:07.460
<i>-Hi.</i>

02:07.502 --> 02:09.254
<i>I want to thank you all
for coming out for this.</i>

02:09.295 --> 02:10.630
<i>I hope
you're enjoying your drinks.</i>

02:10.672 --> 02:13.675
<i></i>

02:15.343 --> 02:17.971
<i>I know that some of you
are still on the fence</i>

02:18.012 --> 02:20.807
<i>about what's going on.</i>

02:20.849 --> 02:23.143
<i>Seems like
this five-letter word, union,</i>

02:23.184 --> 02:25.979
<i>has some of you thinking it's
actually a four-letter word.</i>

02:26.020 --> 02:28.815
<i>-But it's not.</i>

02:28.857 --> 02:30.650
<i>It's a good word.</i>

02:30.692 --> 02:32.277
<i>I assure you.</i>

02:32.318 --> 02:34.654
<i>And I wanted to urge all of you</i>

02:34.696 --> 02:38.825
<i>to join me in voting in favor
