03:05.101 --> 03:07.187
<i>By a long shot.</i>

03:07.228 --> 03:09.647
<i>We are entitled
to medical benefits.</i>

03:09.689 --> 03:12.025
<i>We are entitled to a pension.</i>

03:12.066 --> 03:13.985
<i>And we are entitled
to proper vacation time.</i>

03:14.027 --> 03:16.863
<i>Jeanie Potts,
when your baby's born,</i>

03:16.905 --> 03:19.115
<i>you should be able
to take paid maternity leave</i>

03:19.157 --> 03:21.034
<i>and know that your job
is secure. Am I right?</i>

03:21.075 --> 03:23.536
<i>-Yeah.
- Lisa, you've been working here</i>

03:23.578 --> 03:24.829
<i>for 16 years.</i>

03:24.871 --> 03:26.623
<i>It's crazy
you don't have a pension.</i>

03:26.664 --> 03:29.542
<i>Wouldn't you like
to be able to retire at 66</i>

03:29.584 --> 03:31.377
<i>with something to fall back on?</i>

03:31.419 --> 03:32.879
<i>Or are you gonna be
hunched over that zigzag</i>

03:32.921 --> 03:34.214
<i>for the rest of your life,
hemming dresses</i>

03:34.255 --> 03:35.715
<i>until you're
in your frickin' 70s?</i>

03:35.757 --> 03:37.383
<i>-Look, I've been sewing lace</i>

03:37.425 --> 03:39.469
<i>onto dresses since...</i>

03:41.054 --> 03:42.889
<i>....as long as my son's
been alive.</i>

03:42.931 --> 03:45.058
<i>And I am proud of that work.</i>

03:45.099 --> 03:47.560
<i>Yeah. That's right. Yeah.</i>

03:47.602 --> 03:49.729
<i>We make damn good dresses
at Gelsey's.</i>

03:49.771 --> 03:51.648
<i>-Yeah.
<i>-Hear, hear.</i></i>

03:52.607 --> 03:54.234
<i>Ladies,</i>

03:54.275 --> 03:56.611
<i>these are basic,</i>

03:56.653 --> 04:00.323
<i>fundamental workers' rights
we're asking for.</i>

04:00.365 --> 04:01.741
<i>Yep.</i>

04:01.783 --> 04:04.244
<i>Please stand in solidarity
with me tomorrow</i>

04:04.285 --> 04:07.038
<i>and cast your vote
for unionization.</i>

04:08.248 --> 04:11.042
<i>Let's take control of our lives
for once.</i>

04:11.084 --> 04:12.752
<i></i>

04:17.298 --> 04:19.050
<i>Don't lean on the fence.</i>

04:19.092 --> 04:20.969
<i>It's a good way to get shanked.</i>

