<i>Hey.</i>

04:32.272 --> 04:34.440
<i>It's Bill, right?</i>

04:34.482 --> 04:35.942
<i>-Billy.
- Billy.</i>

04:35.984 --> 04:38.027
<i>My bad. I'm Jerry.</i>

04:38.069 --> 04:39.904
<i>I came to let you know
you're welcome</i>

