to the lab</i>

07:30.700 --> 07:32.076
<i>for testing yet.</i>

07:32.118 --> 07:34.078
<i>Look,
you're not on that case, Chief.</i>

07:36.456 --> 07:38.291
<i>Can I ask you a question, Park?</i>

07:38.332 --> 07:39.959
<i>Very basic question.</i>

07:40.001 --> 07:42.253
<i>Of course.</i>

07:42.295 --> 07:45.131
<i>Whose fucking side are you on?</i>

08:17.246 --> 08:19.540
