by the food line.</i>

08:19.582 --> 08:20.791
<i>Brown eyes, goatee.</i>

08:22.251 --> 08:23.503
<i>Don't look.</i>

08:24.420 --> 08:26.506
<i>Do you know
who I'm talking about?</i>

