<i>Tomorrow,</i>

08:30.593 --> 08:33.304
<i>during the second
mess shift change,</i>

08:33.346 --> 08:35.389
<i>in the hall connecting
that entrance over there</i>

08:35.431 --> 08:37.558
<i>to our cell block--</i>

08:37.600 --> 08:39.185
<i>Look at it.</i>

08:40.186 --> 08:41.687
